title: Exception Thrown When Exporting Data from a Table Inside a Grid Cell
description: When attempting to export data from a table located within a grid cell, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table located within a grid cell, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
EB: When exporting data from two tables, the expected result is that the data should be successfully exported.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Insert a grid containing at least one table within a cell.
2. Attempt to export data from the table(s).
